<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>The Hacking Project</title>
    
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag params[:controller] %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag params[:controller] %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito:400,600,700,800|Roboto:400,500,700" rel="stylesheet"> 

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <%= favicon_link_tag 'favicon.gif' %>

</head>
<body>
  <main class="body-wrap">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar--uppercase  navbar-transparent navbar-inverse">
      <div class="container navbar-container">
        <!-- Brand/Logo -->
        <span class="navbar-brand" href="">
          <%= image_tag 'logothp.png', width: 150 %>
        </span>
        <span class="nav navbar navbar-right align-items-end justify-content-end">
          <a href="#mailer" class="btn btn-styled btn-sm btn-base-1 btn-circle btn-base-5" >
            Inscrire mon mail
          </a>
        </span>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero  -->
    <section class="slice-xxl bg-base-1">
      <div class="container text-center">
          <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                  <div class="fluid-paragraph paragraph-md">
                      <h2 class="heading heading-2 display-1 text-normal strong-600 animated animation-ended c-white">
                        Tu veux t'orienter en programmation web ? Prends de l'avance sur tous les autres 
                      </h2>
                      <br/>
                      <h3 class="heading heading-5 c-white mt-4 strong-300">
                        Rejoins The Hacking Project, le premier bootcamp de code accessible à tous, même les plus novices. Tu vas apprendre à coder en à peine deux mois et demi. 
                      </h3>
                      <br/>
                      <div class="btn-container mt-5">
                        <a href="https://www.thehackingproject.org" class="btn btn-styled btn-lg btn-base-5">Visiter le site</a>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Partie avantage -->
    <section class="slice-xl bg-base-5">
      
    <!-- Section title with lead text -->
    <div class="section-title section-title--style-1 text-center mb-4">
      <h3 class="section-title-inner heading-1 strong-400 c-base-text-5">
        <span>Les points forts</span>
      </h3>
      <div class="fluid-paragraph fluid-paragraph-sm strong-300 text-center">
        La formation a trois avantages :
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="sct-inner container">
        <div class="row cols-xs-space cols-sm-space cols-md-space">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="icon-block icon-block--style-1-v1">
              <div class="block-icon">
                <i class="ion-code-working"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="block-content">
                <h3 class="heading heading-3 c-base-text-5 strong-500">Formation pratique</h3><br/>
                <p class="mt-3">
                  Vous passerez davantage de temps à coder qu'à suivre des cours. Il n'y a pas mieux pour apprendre.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="icon-block icon-block--style-1-v1">
              <div class="block-icon">
                <i class="ion-ios-contact"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="block-content">
                <h3 class="heading heading-3 c-base-text-5 strong-500">Formation peer-learning</h3><br/>
                <p class="mt-3">
                  La formation est basée sur le travail à plusieurs. Ca permet de se motiver, de s'entraider et d'aller plus loin, ensemble.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="icon-block icon-block--style-1-v1">
              <div class="block-icon">
                <i class="ion-ios-body"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="block-content">
                <h3 class="heading heading-3 c-base-text-5 strong-500 center">Formation ouverte à tous</h3><br/>
                <p class="mt-3">
                  Quelque soit votre niveau initial, vous allez apprendre à créer des sites web complets. 
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </section>

    <!-- Partie CTA -->
    <section id="mailer" class="slice-xl bg-base-5">
      <div class="sct-inner container">
        <div class="section-title section-title--style-1 text-center mb-4">
          <h3 class="section-title-inner heading-1 strong-400 c-base-text-5">
            <span>Vous voulez plus d'informations ?</span>
          </h3>
        </div>

        <div class="row col-lg-8 col-lg-push-2">
        <iframe frameborder="50" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://app.mailjet.com/widget/iframe/31dr/6FF" width="100%" height="300"></iframe>
      </div>
    </section>




<footer id="footer" class="footer">
    <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row cols-xs-space cols-sm-space cols-md-space">
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div class="col">
                        <span class="heading heading-sm c-gray-light strong-400">Fait avec patience par deux moussaillons.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="col">
                        <h4 class="heading heading-xs strong-600 text-uppercase mb-1">
                            Restons en contact
                        </h4>

                        <ul class="social-media social-media--style-1-v4">
                            <li>
                                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/thehackingproject/" class="facebook" target="_blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Facebook">
                                    <i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a href="https://www.thehackingproject.org/" class="dribbble" target="_blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Dribbble">
                                    <i class="fa fa-dribbble"></i>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>